Documentation
-------------

:Organization:      Tesla Inc.
:Library Name:      FB_PermIntlk
:Owner:             Mykel Braswell
:Developer(s):      Mykel Braswell, Manuel Goedert
:Date Created:      2020.2.1
:Status:            In-Development
:Description:       FB_PermIntlk provides a way to aggregate several conditions that must be met for some action to begin or continue running.
					When the evaluation of the block is used only to check something before starting, the instance should be named as a permissive.
					When the evaluation of the block is checked continually while an action is occuring, the instance should be named as an interlock.

:JIRA Ticket:       https://issues.teslamotors.com/browse/MASD-3132
:Confluence:        
:Library Repo:      https://stash.teslamotors.com/projects/TWINCAT3/repos/permintlk
:Report Bug:        

.. NOTE:: **Build Version:** This library was developed using TwinCAT Build 3.1.4024.4.

