Documentation
-------------

:Organization:      Tesla Inc.
:Library Name:      FB_Sequencer
:Owner:             Mykel Braswell
:Developer(s):      Mykel Braswell
:Date Created:      2019.3.15
:Status:            In-Development
:Description:       FB_Sequencer provides a way to simply control a step sequence and each individual step with just one function block

:JIRA Ticket:       https://issues.teslamotors.com/browse/MASD-1442
:Confluence:        
:Library Repo:      https://stash.teslamotors.com/projects/TWINCAT3/repos/sequencer
:Report Bug:        

.. NOTE:: **Build Version:** This library was developed using TwinCAT Build 3.1.4024.4.

